{"id":116,"parent_id":95,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":116,"title":"Acts 21","subtitle":"","short_title":"Acts","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 21"],[".studySummary",["i","Paul journeys to Jerusalem—He is persecuted, arrested, and bound."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.1","order":"03.07.021.14173"},["b","1"],"And it came to pass, that after we were gotten from them, and had launched, we came with a straight course unto Coos, and the",["i","day"],"following unto Rhodes, and from thence unto Patara:"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.2","order":"03.07.021.14174"},["b","2"],"And finding a ship sailing over unto Phenicia, we went aboard, and set forth."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.3","order":"03.07.021.14175"},["b","3"],"Now when we had discovered Cyprus, we left it on the left hand, and sailed into Syria, and landed at Tyre: for there the ship was to unlade her burden."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.4","order":"03.07.021.14176"},["b","4"],"And finding disciples, we tarried there seven days: who said to Paul through the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Spirit"],", that he should not go up to Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.5","order":"03.07.021.14177"},["b","5"],"And when we had accomplished those days, we departed and went our way; and they all brought us on our way, with wives and children, till",["i","we were"],"out of the city: and we kneeled down on the shore, and prayed."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.6","order":"03.07.021.14178"},["b","6"],"And when we had taken our leave one of another, we took ship; and they returned home again."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.7","order":"03.07.021.14179"},["b","7"],"And when we had finished",["i","our"],"course from Tyre, we came to Ptolemais, and saluted the brethren, and abode with them one day."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.8","order":"03.07.021.14180"},["b","8"],"And the next",["i","day"],"we that were of Paul’s company departed, and came unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Cæsarea"],": and we entered into the house of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"Philip"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"evangelist"],", which was",["i","one"],"of the seven; and abode with him."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.9","order":"03.07.021.14181"},["b","9"],"And the same man had four daughters, virgins, which did",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"prophesy"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.10","order":"03.07.021.14182"},["b","10"],"And as we tarried",["i","there"],"many days, there came down from Judæa a certain prophet, named Agabus."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.11","order":"03.07.021.14183"},["b","11"],"And when he was come unto us, he took Paul’s girdle, and bound his own hands and feet, and said, Thus saith the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Holy Ghost"],", So shall the Jews at Jerusalem bind the man that owneth this girdle, and shall deliver",["i","him"],"into the hands of the Gentiles."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.12","order":"03.07.021.14184"},["b","12"],"And when we heard these things, both we, and they of that place, besought him not to go up to Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.13","order":"03.07.021.14185"},["b","13"],"Then Paul answered, What mean ye to weep and to break mine heart? for I am ready not to be bound only, but also to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"die"],"at Jerusalem for the name of the Lord Jesus."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.14","order":"03.07.021.14186"},["b","14"],"And when he would not be persuaded, we ceased, saying, The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"will"],"of the Lord be done."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.15","order":"03.07.021.14187"},["b","15"],"And after those days we",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"took up our carriages"],", and went up to Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.16","order":"03.07.021.14188"},["b","16"],"There went with us also",["i","certain"],"of the disciples of Cæsarea, and brought with them one Mnason of Cyprus, an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"old"],"disciple, with whom we should lodge."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.17","order":"03.07.021.14189"},["b","17"],"And when we were come to Jerusalem, the brethren received us gladly."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.18","order":"03.07.021.14190"},["b","18"],"And the",["i","day"],"following Paul went in with us unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"James"],"; and all the elders were present."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.19","order":"03.07.021.14191"},["b","19"],"And when he had saluted them, he declared particularly what things God had wrought among the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Gentiles"],"by his ministry."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.20","order":"03.07.021.14192"},["b","20"],"And when they heard",["i","it,"],"they glorified the Lord, and said unto him, Thou seest, brother, how many thousands of Jews there are which believe; and they are all",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"zealous"],"of the law:"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.21","order":"03.07.021.14193"},["b","21"],"And they are informed of thee, that thou teachest all the Jews which are among the Gentiles to forsake Moses, saying that they ought not to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"circumcise"],["i","their"],"children, neither to walk after the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"customs"],"."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.22","order":"03.07.021.14194"},["b","22"],"What is it therefore? the multitude must needs come together: for they will hear that thou art come."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.23","order":"03.07.021.14195"},["b","23"],"Do therefore this that we say to thee: We have four men which have a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"vow"],"on them;"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.24","order":"03.07.021.14196"},["b","24"],"Them take, and purify thyself with them, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"be"],"at charges with them, that they may",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"shave"],["i","their"],"heads: and all may know that those things, whereof they were informed concerning thee, are nothing; but",["i","that"],"thou thyself also walkest orderly, and keepest the law."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.25","order":"03.07.021.14197"},["b","25"],"As touching the Gentiles which believe, we have written",["i","and"],"concluded that they observe no such thing, save only that they keep themselves from",["i","things"],"offered to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"idols"],", and from blood, and from strangled, and from",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"fornication"],"."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.26","order":"03.07.021.14198"},["b","26"],"Then Paul took the men, and the next day purifying himself with them entered into the temple, to signify the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"accomplishment"],"of the days of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"purification"],", until that an",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_26c"},"offering"],"should be offered for every one of them."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.27","order":"03.07.021.14199"},["b","27"],"And when the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"seven"],"days were almost ended, the Jews which were of Asia, when they saw him in the temple, stirred up all the people, and laid hands on him,"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.28","order":"03.07.021.14200"},["b","28"],"Crying out, Men of Israel, help: This is the man, that teacheth all",["i","men"],"every where against the people, and the law, and this place: and further brought Greeks also into the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"temple"],", and hath",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"polluted"],"this holy place."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.29","order":"03.07.021.14201"},["b","29"],"(For they had seen before with him in the city",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"Trophimus"],"an Ephesian, whom they supposed that Paul had brought into the temple.)"],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.30","order":"03.07.021.14202"},["b","30"],"And all the city was moved, and the people ran together: and they took Paul, and drew him out of the temple: and forthwith the doors were shut."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.31","order":"03.07.021.14203"},["b","31"],"And as they went about to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"kill"],"him, tidings came unto the chief captain of the band, that all Jerusalem was in an",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"uproar"],"."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.32","order":"03.07.021.14204"},["b","32"],"Who immediately took soldiers and centurions, and ran down unto them: and when they saw the chief",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"captain"],"and the soldiers, they left beating of Paul."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.33","order":"03.07.021.14205"},["b","33"],"Then the chief",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"captain"],"came near, and took him, and commanded",["i","him"],"to be bound with two chains; and demanded who he was, and what he had done."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.34","order":"03.07.021.14206"},["b","34"],"And some cried one thing, some another, among the multitude: and when he could not know the certainty for the tumult, he commanded him to be carried into the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"castle"],"."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.35","order":"03.07.021.14207"},["b","35"],"And when he came upon the stairs, so it was, that he was borne of the soldiers for the violence of the people."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.36","order":"03.07.021.14208"},["b","36"],"For the multitude of the people followed after, crying, Away with him."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.37","order":"03.07.021.14209"},["b","37"],"And as Paul was to be led into the castle, he said unto the chief captain, May I speak unto thee? Who said, Canst thou speak Greek?"],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.38","order":"03.07.021.14210"},["b","38"],"Art not thou that Egyptian, which before these days madest an uproar, and leddest out into the wilderness four thousand men that were murderers?"],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.39","order":"03.07.021.14211"},["b","39"],"But Paul said, I am a man",["i","which am"],"a Jew of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_39a"},"Tarsus"],",",["i","a city"],"in Cilicia, a citizen of no mean city: and, I beseech thee, suffer me to speak unto the people."],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.40","order":"03.07.021.14212"},["b","40"],"And when he had given him licence, Paul stood on the stairs, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_40a"},"beckoned"],"with the hand unto the people. And when there was made a great",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_40b"},"silence"],", he spake unto",["i","them"],"in the Hebrew tongue, saying,"]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.4a","order":"03.07.021.14213"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.33"},"D&C 38:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.8a","order":"03.07.021.14215"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/8.40"},"Acts 8:40"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.8b","order":"03.07.021.14217"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.5"},"Acts 6:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/4.11"},"Eph. 4:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.8c","order":"03.07.021.14219"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-tim/4.5"},"2 Tim. 4:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.9a","order":"03.07.021.14221"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/4.4.4-5"},"Judg. 4:4 (4–5)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/2.17"},"Acts 2:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.11a","order":"03.07.021.14223"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/2.18"},"Acts 2:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/11.28.27-28"},"11:28 (27–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.13a","order":"03.07.021.14225"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/20.24"},"Acts 20:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/103.28.27-28"},"D&C 103:28 (27–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.14a","order":"03.07.021.14227"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/26.42"},"Matt. 26:42"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.15a","order":"03.07.021.14229"},["b","15a"],["span.small","GR"],"made preparation, packed baggage."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.16a","order":"03.07.021.14231"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/old-age"},"TG Old Age"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.18a","order":"03.07.021.14233"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/1.19"},"Gal. 1:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.19a","order":"03.07.021.14235"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/11.18"},"Acts 11:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/26.31.11-36"},"Alma 26:31 (11–36)"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.20a","order":"03.07.021.14237"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zeal"},"TG Zeal"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.21a","order":"03.07.021.14239"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/circumcision"},"TG Circumcision"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.21b","order":"03.07.021.14241"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.14"},"Acts 6:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.23a","order":"03.07.021.14243"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vow"},"TG Vow"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.24a","order":"03.07.021.14245"},["b","24a"],["span.small","GR"],"pay expenses for them."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.24b","order":"03.07.021.14247"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/14.8"},"Lev. 14:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/6.18.2-18"},"Num. 6:18 (2–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.25a","order":"03.07.021.14249"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/15.20.19-20"},"Acts 15:20 (19–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.25b","order":"03.07.021.14251"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fornication"},"TG Fornication"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.26a","order":"03.07.021.14253"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/6.13"},"Num. 6:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.26b","order":"03.07.021.14255"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/purification"},"TG Purification"],"."],["div",{"id":"26c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.26c","order":"03.07.021.14257"},["b","26c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/6.11.9-12"},"Num. 6:11 (9–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.27a","order":"03.07.021.14259"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/6.9"},"Num. 6:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.28a","order":"03.07.021.14261"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/24.6"},"Acts 24:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"28b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.28b","order":"03.07.021.14263"},["b","28b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pollution"},"TG Pollution"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.29a","order":"03.07.021.14265"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/20.4"},"Acts 20:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.31a","order":"03.07.021.14267"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.21"},"Acts 26:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/11.26"},"2 Cor. 11:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"31b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.31b","order":"03.07.021.14269"},["b","31b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/rioting-and-reveling"},"TG Rioting and Reveling"],"."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.32a","order":"03.07.021.14271"},["b","32a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.27"},"Acts 23:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.33a","order":"03.07.021.14273"},["b","33a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/24.7"},"Acts 24:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.34a","order":"03.07.021.14275"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.24"},"Acts 22:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"39a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.39a","order":"03.07.021.14277"},["b","39a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.34"},"Acts 23:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"40a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.40a","order":"03.07.021.14279"},["b","40a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/12.17"},"Acts 12:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"40b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.40b","order":"03.07.021.14281"},["b","40b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/silence"},"TG Silence"],"."]]}
